thread.title: Toni-Maree Hoogendoorn
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Toni-Maree Hoogendoorn

author: Toni-Maree Hoogendoorn
title: Toni-Maree Hoogendoorn
text: Fees to collect our items was nearly equivalent to a months rent. We had to pay in advance but apparently were not entitled to receive excess monies we had paid in advance. Was handy at the time as we did not have time to shop around. Unfortunately would not recommend as in the end we were ripped off.
